192471: Refill Prescription
Example: Can you please refill my Fluoxine and when will I be able to pick it up?

310472: Submit new prescription
Example: My doctor will be calling in a prescription for Vannagat this afternoon - please fill it ASAP.

461749: Check insurance coverage
Example: I've been prescribed Tikifeer, what is my coverage for that? What will it cost out of pocket?

018927: Update payment method
Example: I need you to remove the credit card ending in 1083 from autopay on my account

951783: Medication interaction query
Example: I've been taking Troclyn for the last week and I have a migraine. Is it safe to take some Gurilil to help? 

014738: Login issues
Example: Reset my password

104928: None
Example: Do you sell ice cream?

Classify the following message received by an online pharmacy. Output the intent of the message in a json containing the number corresponding to the applicable intent. 

Message: To Whom it May Concern, 

I am a pharmeceutical representative for Fryosook. I see that you do not carry our flagship product, Cerance, but do provide the generic chlorophebatyl. I would love to schedule a call to discuss the benefits of supplying directly through us. We are passionate about Cerance and helping as many people as possible. Please feel free to call my a 384-195-1385 to discuss further. 

Best, 

Hailey Smalls
